custom_fields.label: Transport Receipt Date
custom_fields.mandatory_depends_on: eval:in_list(["Registered Regular", "SEZ", "Overseas", "Deemed Export"], doc.gst_category) && in_list(["Air", "Ship", "Rail"], doc.mode_of_transport)
custom_fields.name: Sales Invoice-lr_date

custom_fields.label: Transport Receipt No
custom_fields.mandatory_depends_on: eval:in_list(["Registered Regular", "SEZ", "Overseas", "Deemed Export"], doc.gst_category) && in_list(["Air", "Ship", "Rail"], doc.mode_of_transport)
custom_fields.name: Sales Invoice-lr_no
